Class Yossaria

  • java.lang.Object
    • AbstractFurniture
      • Cabinet
        • Yossaria

  • public class Yossaria
extends Cabinet
    This class extends the AbstractCabinet class and represents a Yossaria cabinet that sets a number of details--size, color options, and maximum number of shelves.
